Package com.aurel.track.fieldType.runtime.base

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ICustomFieldTypeRT
    Base interface for all custom fields defining their runtime behavior
    IFieldTypeRT
    Base interface for all fields (system and custom) defining their runtime behavior
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractFieldTypeRT
    The base class for runtime field types with typical default implementations
    CompositeComparable
    Class for sorting the composite values The parts of the composite are sorted one by one until a different sort order is found at a certain level
    CustomCompositeBaseRT
    A custom composite field is a composite of other custom single fields It is itself a CustomFieldTypeRT
    CustomOnePieceBaseRT  
    CustomSelectComparable
    Class for sorting the simple custom list entries The sortOrder is not enough because we can't be sure that only one list is involved for this field in different contexts The sortOrder is local in a list, so it can happen that two entries from different lists have the same sortOrder, consequently by sorting/grouping the different values might be mixed just because they have the same sortOrder TODO we do not take into account multiple selections.
    DropDownContainer
    Used by rendering the lists (IFieldTypeRT.processLoadDataSource()), and as lookup maps for select keys IFieldTypeRT.getShowValue(), IFieldTypeRT.getShowISOValue(), IFieldTypeRT.getSortOrderValue()
    FieldChange  
    FieldsManagerRT
    Manager class for defining the business logic for fields at runtime
    InputFieldTypeRT  
    LocalLookupContainer
    Contains lookups specific for the item result set (should be loaded for each result set) The global lookups (lists) are accessible through the LookupContainer Used in getShowValue() for getting the project specific itemID, calculating the WBS
    LookupContainer
    Used by rendering the lists (IFieldTypeRT.processLoadDataSource()), and as lookup maps for select keys IFieldTypeRT.getShowValue(), IFieldTypeRT.getShowISOValue(), IFieldTypeRT.getSortOrderValue()
    OutputFieldTypeRT  
    SelectContext  
    SerializableBeanAllowedContext  
    SystemInputBaseRT
    Base class for read/write runtime system fields
    SystemOutputBaseRT
    Base class for read only runtime system fields
    WBSComparable
    Class for sorting the composite values The parts of the composite are sorted one by one until a different sort order is found at a certain level
    WorkItemContext
    Transfer object between the controler (action) and the business logic
